reviewText: I actually thought it was a book so I was disappointed when the DVD arrived
Thanks for the speedy shipment. Exactly what I wanted.

These videos were St. Patrick's Day gifts for  my Irish friends.  However, I took a 'sneak peek' at one of them before wrapping it and found  it be be a beautiful scenic  and poetic portrayal  of Ireland.  A great addition to anyone's video library.
